@page "/"

<PageTitle>Scrape</PageTitle>

<div class="container mt-4">
    <h1 class="text-center">Web Scraping Tool</h1>
    <p class="text-muted text-center">
        This application allows you to extract data from websites effortlessly.
        Enter your search criteria, specify optional date ranges, and let the tool do the rest.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-4">
        <h3>Features:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Extract data based on specific search text.</li>
            <li>Filter results by date range (optional).</li>
            <li>View extracted URLs, content, emails, and links.</li>
            <li>Powered by advanced web automation techniques.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4">
        <h3>How to Use:</h3>
        <ol>
            <li>Navigate to the <a href="/mdpisite">Scrape</a> page.</li>
            <li>Enter your search text and optional date range.</li>
            <li>Click the "Extract" button to start the process.</li>
            <li>View the status and results of the extraction.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4">
        <h3>About:</h3>
        <p>
            This tool is built using Blazor and .NET 8, leveraging modern web technologies
            to provide a seamless and efficient scraping experience.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>


